《'''Verax'''》是2013年[[香港|香港]]短片，描写[[爱德华·斯诺登|爱德华·斯诺登]]危机。<ref name=AFPSnowdenfilm>[http://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/article/1272335/hong-kong-amateur-filmmakers-produce-worlds-first-edward-snowden-film "Hong Kong amateur filmmakers produce world's first Edward Snowden film"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/article/1272335/hong-kong-amateur-filmmakers-produce-worlds-first-edward-snowden-film |date=20130702100726 }}. 《[[南华早报|南华早报]]》. 《[[法新社|法新社]]》. 2013-06-30. Retrieved 2013-06-30.</ref>制片人是謝夫·發露（Jeff Floro）、李健恩（Edwin Lee）、謝兆龍（Shawn Tse）和崔正傑（Marcus Tsui）。<ref name=FraterSnowdeliv>Frater, Patrick. "[http://variety.com/2013/digital/news/snowden-film-team-delivers-digital-snapshot-1200503490/ Snowden YouTube Film Delivers Digital Snapshot] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/6WwGTN3Jy?url=http://variety.com/2013/digital/news/snowden-film-team-delivers-digital-snapshot-1200503490/ |date=20150311024326 |dateformat=iso }}." 《[[綜藝|綜藝]]》. 2013-07-01. Retrieved on 2013-07-02.</ref>他們上載這段短片至[[YouTube|YouTube]]。<ref name=AFPSnowdenfilm/>

